Install Mesh creator gmsh (www.http://gmsh.info/).
Binaries are available for all operating systems + ubuntu supports it via
`sudo apt-get install gmsh`

Make sure numpy, matplotlib, scipy are installed.

Install python mesh interfaces: pip install pygmsh meshio

Install pysparse:
pip install -e git://pysparse.git.sourceforge.net/gitroot/pysparse/pysparse#egg=PySparse
Linux/Unix only!

Install fipy:
pip install ez_setup
pip install fipy